<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10421829>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Tachycines (Gymnaeta) lingulatus sp. nov. (male). A. habitus, dorsal view; B. habitus, lateral view; C. habitus, ventral view; D. head, frontal view; E. pronotum, dorsal view; F. hind tarsus, lateral view; G. genitalia, dorsal view; H. genitalia, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10421829/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10421833>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Tachycines (Gymnaeta) lingulatus sp. nov. (female). A. habitus, dorsal view; B. habitus, lateral view; C. habitus, ventral view; D. ovipositor, lateral view; E. subgenital plate, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10421833/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10421835>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. The shape of female subgenital plates of four Tachycines (Gymnaeta) species. A. subgenital plate of T. (G.) chenhui, after Rampini et al. (2008); B. subgenital plate of T. (G.) cavernus, after Jiao et al. (2008); C. subgenital plate of T. (G.) zorzini, after Rampini et al. (2008); D. subgenital plate of T. (G.) lalinus, after Feng et al. (2019)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10421835/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

